{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/WSL2-with-VSCode","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"6429fc04-e09a-5442-b5f5-0fce45f76226","html":"<h2 id=\"개요\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%9C%EC%9A%94\" aria-label=\"개요 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>개요</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>윈도우10에서 VSCode와 우분투(Ubuntu) 개발환경을 설정하는 방법</li>\n<li>기준 환경 : Windows 10 64bit 및 <strong>WSL2</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"윈도우-최신버전-업데이트\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9C%88%EB%8F%84%EC%9A%B0-%EC%B5%9C%EC%8B%A0%EB%B2%84%EC%A0%84-%EC%97%85%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8\" aria-label=\"윈도우 최신버전 업데이트 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>윈도우 최신버전 업데이트</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>윈도우 설정 -> 업데이트 확인 -> 설치 -> (요구시) 재부팅 -> 반복</li>\n<li>업데이트 더이상 안 뜰 때까지 <strong>반복</strong></li>\n<li>완료 시에도 Windows10 Version <strong>2004</strong> 이상 버전이 아닐 경우 아래 사이트에서 수동 업데이트</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/ko-kr/software-download/windows10\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://www.microsoft.com/ko-kr/software-download/windows10</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"wsl2-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#wsl2-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"wsl2 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>WSL2 설치</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.dalso.org/linux/wsl2/11099\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://blog.dalso.org/linux/wsl2/11099</a> 참조</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"windows-terminal-편의-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#windows-terminal-%ED%8E%B8%EC%9D%98-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"windows terminal 편의 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Windows Terminal 편의 설정</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>기본 탭 WSL로 변경</p>\n<ul>\n<li>“defaultProfile” 값을 Ubuntu의 guid 값과 일치시켜준다</li>\n<li>프로파일 순서를 바꿔서 Ubuntu를 첫번째로 해주는 것도 편하다</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>기본 디렉토리를 WSL 홈으로 변경</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ubuntu 프로파일에 다음사항 추가 <code class=\"language-text\">&quot;startingDirectory&quot;: &quot;//wsl$/Ubuntu/home/{유저명}&quot;</code></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/microsoft/terminal/issues/2849\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://github.com/microsoft/terminal/issues/2849</a> 참조</li>\n<li>안 될 경우, CPU의 BIOS 세팅을 확인한다 <a href=\"https://friendcom.tistory.com/585\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://friendcom.tistory.com/585</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>setting.json 예시</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">{\n...\n&quot;defaultProfile&quot;: &quot;{2c4de342-38b7-51cf-b940-2309a097f518}&quot;, // 하단 Ubuntu 프로파일과 guid 일치 시켜 줌\n...\n&quot;profiles&quot;:\n{\n  ...\n  &quot;list&quot;:\n  [\n      {\n          &quot;guid&quot;: &quot;{2c4de342-38b7-51cf-b940-2309a097f518}&quot;,\n          &quot;hidden&quot;: false,\n          &quot;name&quot;: &quot;Ubuntu&quot;,\n          &quot;source&quot;: &quot;Windows.Terminal.Wsl&quot;,\n          &quot;startingDirectory&quot;: &quot;//wsl$/Ubuntu/home/kang&quot; // 기본 디렉토리 설정\n      },\n      {\n          &quot;guid&quot;: &quot;{61c54bbd-c2c6-5271-96e7-009a87ff44bf}&quot;,\n          &quot;name&quot;: &quot;Windows PowerShell&quot;,\n          ...</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"vs-code-설치-및-초기-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#vs-code-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98-%EB%B0%8F-%EC%B4%88%EA%B8%B0-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"vs code 설치 및 초기 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>VS Code 설치 및 초기 설정</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://code.visualstudio.com/</a></li>\n<li>좌측 extension 메뉴 -> remote development extension pack 검색 및 설치</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"지역-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A7%80%EC%97%AD-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"지역 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>지역 설정</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>카카오 미러 설정</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">sudo sed -i &#39;s/archive.ubuntu.com/mirror.kakao.com/g&#39; /etc/apt/sources.list \\\nsudo sed -i &#39;s/security.ubuntu.com/mirror.kakao.com/g&#39; /etc/apt/sources.list \\\nsudo apt-get update</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>한국 로케일 설정 <a href=\"https://beomi.github.io/2017/07/10/Ubuntu-Locale-to-ko_KR/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://beomi.github.io/2017/07/10/Ubuntu-Locale-to-ko_KR/</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>위 설정 완료 후, 최종적으로 <code class=\"language-text\">LANG=ko_KR.UTF-8</code> 입력하고 ~/.bashrc 최하단에도 입력</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"wsl-원격-개발-환경-구동\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#wsl-%EC%9B%90%EA%B2%A9-%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C-%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD-%EA%B5%AC%EB%8F%99\" aria-label=\"wsl 원격 개발 환경 구동 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>WSL 원격 개발 환경 구동</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>선행 사항 완료 후 Windows terminal 로 WSL 쉘(Ubuntu) 접속</li>\n<li>\n<p>workspace 디렉토리 생성하여 해당 위치로 이동</p>\n<ul>\n<li>~/workspace 추천</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>해당 디렉토리에서 VS Code 실행 <code class=\"language-text\">code .</code></li>\n<li>좌측 하단 <strong>WSL: Ubuntu</strong> 배너 확인되면 성공</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/WSL2-with-VSCode","tagSlugs":["/tag/개발툴/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-08-06T17:15:00.000Z","description":"윈도우10에서 VSCode와 Ubuntu 개발환경 설정","tags":["개발툴"],"title":"WSL2 (Windows Subsystem Linux 2) 환경에서 VSCode 사용하기","socialImage":"/media/image-2.jpg"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/WSL2-with-VSCode"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","3942705351","401334301"]}